#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
Zero Python Provision (ZPP) — Hardened Resilient Edition
Version: 0.2.1

Single-file Ubuntu/Debian provisioner that:
- installs only missing packages
- continues section-by-section on failure
- logs every action
- prints and writes a final summary report
- avoids risky Python system mutation by default
"""

